\s TURASOMA MW’IJAMBO RY’UHORAHO
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Turasoma mw’ijambo ry’Uhoraho, yuko Aburahamu yizeye Imana imukura mu gihugu c’iwabo imwereka igihugu c’isezerano, kubw’ukwizera yaraciboneye.\bd*
\pc \bdit Nawe mwene Data, n’utahure yuko \bdit*\bdit Ukwizera\bdit*\bdit , ar’ukumenya rwose ivyizigirwa, udakekeranya, n’ibitabonwa nikwo kubitumenyesha, kuko kutubwira, kw’ar’ivy’ukuri.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Mbega ukwizera, sikwo kwanatumye Abera b’Imana, bashikira neza, ivy’Imana yabasezeranira, bakagendana nayo itaboneka, gushika naho Henoki azamurwa.\bd*
\pc \bdit Nawe mwene Data, n’utahure yuko \bdit*\bdit Ukwizera\bdit*\bdit , ar’ukumenya rwose ivyizigirwa, udakekeranya, n’ibitabonwa nikwo kubitumenyesha, kuko kutubwira, kw’ar’ivy’ukuri.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Ukwizera nikwo kwatumye, Nowa yumvira ijwi ry’Umwami Imana nzima, akubaka ubwato bamucokora gushika naho umwuzure waza, agakira n’abamwumviye bose.\bd*
\pc \bdit Nawe mwene Data, n’utahure yuko \bdit*\bdit Ukwizera\bdit*\bdit , ar’ukumenya rwose ivyizigirwa, udakekeranya, n’ibitabonwa nikwo kubitumenyesha, kuko kutubwira, kw’ar’ivy’ukuri.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Kandi yemwe hanga ry’Imana nzima, ukwizera kwatumye Daniyeli, naho yatawe mu rwobo rw’intambwe, asohoka ari muzima vy’ukuri, kuko ukwizera kunesha imana\bd*\bd .\bd*
\pc \bdit Nawe mwene Data, n’utahure yuko \bdit*\bdit Ukwizera\bdit*\bdit , ar’ukumenya rwose ivyizigirwa, udakekeranya, n’ibitabonwa nikwo kubitumenyesha, kuko kutubwira, kw’ar’ivy’ukuri.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd None mvuge ikindi ki ku kwizera, kuko n’ababaye abahizi bose, babishobojwe n’ukwizera Imana, bene Data nimuze twizere, tuzobane n’Umwami ibihe vyose.\bd*
